{"tid":38324,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[安已不］爸爸入左醫院","createTime":"2016-12-14T00:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T16:11:06.000Z","uid":11854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c7b8ec5cc50d77f7a6e372c6da56511134d4a9","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:31:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的&hellip;前日老豆入左醫院⋯但我唔知要點做<br />\n例如<br />\n問老豆而加嘅情況<br />\n幾時問同問邊個<br />\n暫時只係知道爸爸腎炎發緊燒&hellip;<br />\n比親戚煩到我唔知應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求各位巴絲為小女子指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e1aecfa93f3982dafcdd158941ee19ea93fa49","tid":38324,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:44:35.000Z","msg":"採病時間問護士<br />\n<br />\n護士有塊版寫哂發生咩事<br />\n<br />\nBtw祝你老豆早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73617dcbd3fcc89336ff9cc0332345fed584a01b","tid":38324,"uid":9238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"我爸之前住左好耐廣華，可能可以答到你<br />\n你可以揀問護士，好似上面巴打咁講<br />\n但通常護士唔會答到你好多野<br />\n如果想問醫生嘅，可以試下<br />\n1. 探病時同護士講留低電話話想問醫生野，正常個醫生就會覆返你，不過我都試過個醫生忙，幾日都唔覆<br />\n2. 唔好理個探病時間，問吓護士醫生幾點巡房，通常係朝早，你就去定伏佢"},{"pid":"38e9dc65bbd729d57127e6db81d6adf7386fb8e2","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:09:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多謝兩位巴絲指教⋯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb5b9c7e5d556721ae52a87d58edf7fb96cf46a","tid":38324,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"我係過來人，想問啲咩，睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce5587fd79261eab3f359647a13376a3df0425e","tid":38324,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a604f520b41d01728cf711a71104f6160333db53","tid":38324,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"其實你唔強調小女<br />\n會唔會有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c8114621d54cb53dab550d0a52b019bf0b30bc","tid":38324,"uid":14842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你唔強調小女<br />\n會唔會有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，應該啲人會屌住覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec2caa8a69b082566c5b1b8c6c949020dde80ce","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><blockquote>其實你唔強調小女<br />\n會唔會有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，應該啲人會屌住覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啊&hellip;會唔會係咁&hellip;<br />\nBtw 爸爸已經退左燒啦～醫生就話係急性腎炎⋯同埋再抽左血去check 啦應該差唔多出院啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">另外好多謝各巴絲幫忙解答連登真係一個好有愛嘅地方</span></span></div><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463d759d671e558f721bf8d293c4f1baeffdedc7","tid":38324,"uid":15796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我爸之前住左好耐廣華，可能可以答到你<br />\n你可以揀問護士，好似上面巴打咁講<br />\n但通常護士唔會答到你好多野<br />\n如果想問醫生嘅，可以試下<br />\n1. 探病時同護士講留低電話話想問醫生野，正常個醫生就會覆返你，不過我都試過個醫生忙，幾日都唔覆<br />\n2. 唔好理個探病時間，問吓護士醫生幾點巡房，通常係朝早，你就去定伏佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非探病時間咪撚上嚟阻住晒"},{"pid":"f77f1a9ce0e1196dc0d23be19310d87ba7d41e60","tid":38324,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"唔好伏我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估我地有時間唔會解釋比你地聽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f8d950576e79ff06a36d951926b175cc3a8f7b","tid":38324,"uid":13837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"急性腎炎<br />\n起碼燒完又退 退完又爆 不斷Loop兩至三日先好<br />\n唔好急住出院 吊多兩日鹽水 清哂腎啲細菌安全啲<br />\n呢家最好就係飲多啲水⋯<br />\n<br />\n利申：急性腎炎入過兩次醫院"},{"pid":"600af285241d5a7c1a2ba00bcc5925ade31dde22","tid":38324,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:44:20.000Z","msg":"1. 探病時間問護士<br />\n2. 探病時間同護士講想聯絡醫生<br />\n<br />\n巡房醫生好撚忙，唔好阻住醫生<br />\n將心比己，如果有其他病人家屬阻住醫生巡房，令你老豆成朝都見唔到醫生，得唔適時既治療，你會點?"},{"pid":"32c49b2f042f77cefff98bcedc923547548b8c92","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好伏我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估我地有時間唔會解釋比你地聽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係好感動呀麻～（淚奔"},{"pid":"7a82a00d3e66dbb6a0c2b774b5060b3ccd263560","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急性腎炎<br />\n起碼燒完又退 退完又爆 不斷Loop兩至三日先好<br />\n唔好急住出院 吊多兩日鹽水 清哂腎啲細菌安全啲<br />\n呢家最好就係飲多啲水⋯<br />\n<br />\n利申：急性腎炎入過兩次醫院</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係爸爸覺得自己出得姐⋯應該都要等埋血報告先知出唔出得～但點樣要求吊多兩日鹽水？佢話佢有好多水⋯同埋我見佢只係著醫院衫出汗但唔算熱架，係米會咁架？"},{"pid":"6410b3ec53e9e1b33b1c206bf4072b099fc3724c","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 探病時間問護士<br />\n2. 探病時間同護士講想聯絡醫生<br />\n<br />\n巡房醫生好撚忙，唔好阻住醫生<br />\n將心比己，如果有其他病人家屬阻住醫生巡房，令你老豆成朝都見唔到醫生，得唔適時既治療，你會點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白呀所以都係問護士炸"},{"pid":"304c4a25d79389d7f8ffd71f338ff40e6044d29b","tid":38324,"uid":15796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 探病時間問護士<br />\n2. 探病時間同護士講想聯絡醫生<br />\n<br />\n巡房醫生好撚忙，唔好阻住醫生<br />\n將心比己，如果有其他病人家屬阻住醫生巡房，令你老豆成朝都見唔到醫生，得唔適時既治療，你會點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白呀所以都係問護士炸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以護士唔忙？"},{"pid":"27d64b07281ddf7a74fede874c3969e74a1fb828","tid":38324,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"急性腎炎處理得唔好會發展成慢性腎衰竭，好唔返，最終要洗腎。<br />\n<br />\n不過醫生畀得你出院就表示安全，但以後都要小心復發，因為發得多啲組織可能會結疤，影響正常運作，甚至可以演變至腎衰竭，定期驗身啦。"},{"pid":"12c6d274e761aaac25037eeb3d259e83f9e6831d","tid":38324,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急性腎炎處理得唔好會發展成慢性腎衰竭，好唔返，最終要洗腎。<br />\n<br />\n不過醫生畀得你出院就表示安全，但以後都要小心復發，因為發得多啲組織可能會結疤，影響正常運作，甚至可以演變至腎衰竭，定期驗身啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}